Have Apache Tomcat V7
install derby 10.1
Go in cmd -> type startNetworkServer  ( derby should be started).
Open Eclipse Luna.
GO in import, choose git --> provide clone URL.
Open project in eclipse.
Add a new server ( tomcat v7.0).
Make a new database connection from data source explorer choosing derby 10.1 option and locating derbyclient.jar jar file.
Run the queries in db.sql file to run initial queries for the site.

